hello.. how can i set it up to ps3? cuz folder have many files

First of all you need to have a custom Firmware installed on your PS3, like: kmeaw 3.55 CFW or Waninkoko V2 CWF 3.55. Put the multiman .PKG files into a usbmemory, plug it in your usb-port on your PS3 and install from there
